toc.title: Compiler User Guide
toc.description: Comprehensive user guide for SDCC (Small Device C Compiler), a free open source ISO C11/C17 compiler suite targeting 8-bit microcontrollers including 8051, Z80, R800, STM8, and PIC architectures. This manual provides essential information about compiler installation, usage, programming techniques, data types, memory models, optimization strategies, and MCU-specific development practices for embedded systems programming.
